comments: Doncic (DAL) and HIll (MIL) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Hill (MIL) cleanly deflects the ball away from Doncic (DAL).
Kleber (DAL) and Antetokounmpo (MIL) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Hill (MIL) is already in Finney-Smith's (DAL) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Finney-Smith (DAL) places his left hand on Antetokounmpo's (MIL) shoulder and swipes his right arm down, making contact with Antetokounmpo's arm during the shot attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) jumps A to B into Porzingis (DAL) and affects his shot near the rim.
Porzingis (DAL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Lopez (MIL) in the post.
Middleton (MIL) briefly grasps and immediately releases Porzingis' (DAL) jersey during the inbound.
Middleton (MIL) makes marginal contact with Doncic (DAL) as he is passing the ball.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) fails to fully clear the lane and is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Kleber (DAL) and Hill (MIL) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Porzingis (DAL) is bracing himself for the contact from Matthews (MIL) and releases away from the contact.
Porzingis (DAL) and Antetokounmpo (MIL) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.  Porzingis cleanly deflects the ball away from Bledsoe (MIL).
Replay review of the shooting foul called on Antetokounmpo (MIL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. The foul is issued to Middleton (MIL) as the result of the challenge.
Finney-Smith (DAL) places his hand momentarily on Middleton's (MIL) hip before correcting.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) places his hand momentarily on Hill's (MIL) hip before correcting.
Lopez (MIL) and Porzingis (DAL) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) and Antetokounmpo (MIL) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Doncic (DAL) is bracing himself for the contact from Bledsoe (MIL) and releases away from the contact.
Bledsoe (MIL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Doncic (DAL) on the perimeter.
Connaughton (MIL) makes marginal contact with Porzingis' (DAL) body without affecting his shot attempt.
Porzingis (DAL) moves into Antetokounmpo's (MIL) body and affects his shot near the rim.
Bledsoe (MIL) makes contact to Doncic's (DAL) arm as he is passing the ball.
Middleton (MIL) makes contact to Kleber's (DAL) arm as he defends the shot near the rim.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) does not veer unnaturally into Finney-Smith's (DAL) body as Finney-Smith attempts to defend the pass.
Finney-Smith (DAL) does not make contact to Middleton's (MIL) arm as he defends the pass.
DiVincenzo (MIL) and Doncic (DAL) briefly engage and disengage as Doncic receives the ball on the perimeter.
Doncic (DAL) is bracing himself for the contact from DiVincenzo (MIL) and releases away from the contact.
DiVincenzo (MIL) is moving alongside Doncic's (DAL) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive.
DiVincenzo (MIL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Doncic (DAL) on the perimeter.
Middleton (MIL) and Finney-Smith (DAL) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Bledsoe (MIL) is moving alongside Doncic's (DAL) path to the basket and maintains a legal guarding position.
Bledsoe (MIL) legally contests Doncic's (DAL) shot attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) is already in Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) commits a take foul on Finney-Smith (DAL).
